file: MessageStartEvent.php
class: "Ineersa\\AgentCore\\Domain\\Event\\Lifecycle\\MessageStartEvent"
type: readonly final class
summary: Represents a domain event signaling the initiation of message processing within the lifecycle. This immutable value object encapsulates the context required to track the start of a message operation. It serves as a structural marker for event sourcing and domain audit trails.
